    "body": "### Feature description\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/yorickpeterse/nvim-pqf shows a cosmetic/layout/UI improvement for the quickfix list:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1359421/136468284-a42c88b5-65e2-463e-9cc7-55d4c87bdae6.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Proposal\r\n\r\nThese seem like \"easy wins\" that could be done by default in Nvim quickfix list:\r\n\r\n1. Rendering the column/line numbers in `c:l` format\r\n    - should probably done via **conceal** in case plugins depend on the legacy format\r\n2. aligning the text\r\n\r\ncc @YorickPeterse",
