        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "@clason `warning` is the raw input value. As a starting point we should make the smallest change possible, which includes _not_ remapping item kinds (e.g. `warning` to `warn`, `error` to `err`, etc). Instead we just show whatever the given value is. If users want to do any remapping it's bound to become subjective, and that's best done in a plugin.",
